Exercise 4:

Trace the following code, to find and solve the syntax error. You need to identify the mistake and rewrite the correct code.  
while (int i = 0; i <= 100; i++) {
			if (i % 5 == 0) {
				System.out.println(i);
			}
			
		}




Exercise 5: 

Trace the following code, to find and solve the syntax error. You need to identify the mistake and rewrite the correct code.  
